---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage content sources

Usage: mf source [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list      List sources [aliases: ls]
  new       Create a source
  update    Update a source
  index     Index sources
  remove    Remove a source [aliases: rm]
  rename    Rename a source
  clean     Clean source index
  show      Show source details
  advanced  Manage advanced LanceDB-backed Sources (enable, sync, enrich, model, skill)

Options:
      --root <PATH>      Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>    Config file path
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose output
  -q, --quiet            Silence non-error output
  -o, --output <FORMAT>  Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --json             Shorthand for --output json
      --no-color         Disable colored output
  -p, --project <NAME>   Project name for project-scoped operations
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
